title: How to: Potions
author: DrazVietor
pages:
#- ===== How To ======
===== POTIONS =====

Book by fuckin' Draziw



Make yo fuckin' loadouts EZPZ with this GUIDE 2 FUCKIN POTS.
#- Contents.

1. Mechanics
2. Recipies
3. Load outs & You: How to Not Fuck It All Up
4. Material Masterlist
5. Final Note
#-             MECHANICS!
===================

Potions apply debuffs and buffs to other motherfuckers and yourself. Two broad types are hostile and friendly. Everybody is hostile, and you can hurt yourself. SO DONT FUCK UP, YOU STUPID MOTHERFUC
#- Types of Potions.
1. Normal
2. Extended 
3. Level II
4. Corrupted
5. Splash

Splash can be any of the four above it, but will reduce the duration of certain potions. Level II Potions are always much shorter.
#- Drinkable Potions
- It takes time to drink it. Slows you down, so don't fuckin drink a potion if youre gettin fuckin focused.

Splash Potions
- Aim them PROPERLY. Don't fuckin slow your teammates or yourself. Don't give regen to enemy.
#- 

Now that you know how to not HURT YOURSELF, here's how to fuckin make potions.


#-         RECIPIES
===================

Every potion starts with a water bottle. Get your stands set up in sets of 3s to make things easier for storage and counting. Make a water well next to your potion station. Aquire glass bottles. Build brewing stands.
#- Recipes in order:

1. Fire Res
2. Water Breathing
3. Swiftness
4. Healing
5. Poison
6. Night Vision
7. Regeneration
8. Strength
9. Invisibility
10. Weakness
11. Slowness
#-      MATERIAL KEY

CORRUPT - Fermented Spider Eye
EXTENDED - Redstone
LEVEL II - Glowstone Dust
FERMENTED SPIDER EYE: 1 Spider Eye, 1 Brown Mushroom, 1 Sugar
GLISTENING MELON: 8 Golden Nuggets, 1 Melon Slice
#- GOLDEN CARROT: 8 Golden Nuggets, 1 Carrot
MAGMA CREAM: Blaze Powder, Slimball

BREWING STAND

          BLAZEROD
    COB      COB    COB
    BLE      BLE    BLE
#-          FIRE RESISTANCE
Immunity to Fire, Lava, Blaze attacks.

Add Nether Wart to 3 Water Bottles for Awkward Potions. 
Awk Pot > Magma Cream

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH: DON'T
CORRUPT: Slowness
#-        WATER BREATHING
Adds water breathing for 3min - 8min.

Awk Pot > Pufferfish

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH : DON'T
CORRUPT: NO
#-        SWIFTNESS POTION
Increases movement, sprint, and jumping length by 20-40% for 3min-8min.

Awk Potion > Sugar

EXTENDED:  YES (8MIN)
LEVEL II: YES (40%)
SPLASH: USE LEVEL 2
CORRUPT: Slowness
#-            HEALING POTION
Replaces 2 - 4 hearts.

Awk Pot > Glistening Melon

EXTENDED: NO
LEVEL II: DO THIS
SPLASH: YES PLS
CORRUPT: Harming

The staple of every loadout.
#-           POISON POTION
Poisons the player, reducing half a heart every 1.5 seconds and being REALLY FUCKING ANNOYING.

Awk Pot > Spider Eye
EXTENDED: SATAN
LEVEL II: SATAN
SPLASH: HITLER SATAN
CORRUPT: NO
don't drink it, you fuck.
#-                NIGHT VISION Gammabright.

Awk Pot > Golden Carrot

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH: WHY PLS NO
CORRUPT: Invisibility

Don't fuckin waste carrots. 
#-              REGENERATION Restores 1 heart every 1.2 - 2.4 seconds for .16 - 2min

Awk Pot > Ghast Tear

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: YES
SPLASH: SITUATIONAL
CORRUPT: Weakness

Important potion.
#-          STRENGTH POTION
Increases damage by 130% - 260% for 1.30 - 8min.

Awk Pot > Blaze Powder

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: YES
SPLASH: DON'T
CORRUPT: Weakness
#- (CORRUPT) INVISIBLITY
Vanish! Except your weapons & armor is still visible.

Potion of Night Vision > Fermented Spider Eye

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH: NO

Bypassed by Radar.
#- (CORRUPT) WEAKNESS
Reduces melee attacks by 0.5 damage.

Potion of Regen OR STR Potion > Fermented Spider Eye

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH: YES

Don't hit yourself.
#- (CORRUPT) SLOWNESS
Movement reduced to crouch speed for 1.30min - 3min.

Pot of Swift OR Pot of Fire Res > Fermented Spider Eye

EXTENDED: YES
LEVEL II: NO
SPLASH: YES
Good for escapes.
#-     Loadouts & You:
  How Not to Fuck Up
===================So you're supplying cool pvpers with 'loadouts'. Cool. Read on for rough estimates you should keep on hand atleast 90% of the time. Don't store 'normal level' potions, pleb. POT N GO, KIDDO!
#- Author Note: Train your potion throwing on CivPvP. Srsly.

The following potions are found in every loadout, but at different amounts.

FIRE RES: For protection against Flame Bows/Swords. Keep a singlechest.
#- STR Potions: Keep a single chest of extended, double of Level II. 

Regen: 2 double chests of extended. Do it! Maybe some Splash II. Or Level II. Depends on if you are Hitler.

Speed Potions: Keep a double chest of each
#- kind, and include atleast 18+ Speed 2 Splash. For crossing long distance on horse, it's a secret cheat to going FUCKING RETARDEDLY FAST.

Healing Pots: Splash. Unless Level 2 and you're pro as fuck. Go you, kiddo. Keep 2 doublechest of these.
#- Night Vision, Water Breathing: Don't waste space with these. Get Respiration on your helmet. 

Invisi: No, other potions are better most of the time.

Splash Corrupt: Keep a single chest of each.

#- There you go, buddy. You've got yourself a good emergency stock. Feel good about yourself. Take care of yourself. I care about you.



Deeply. 

Very deeply.
